{"tid":1447814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好叫黑社會，叫恐怖份子","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:18:26.000Z","uid":62270,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ad2003417b8b5792a99d9ddb0e1459086ecd646e","tid":1447814,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:13:41.000Z","msg":"唔好叫警犬，黑社會，而家直頭係邪惡組織，係恐怖份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cbc6971c28de2e8a995dc8e81b74697cde160e","tid":1447814,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:13:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf727c3ca6f25dfa197802250ddd99f65f7f4266","tid":1447814,"uid":103783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:14:17.000Z","msg":"解散香港警隊 制裁戰爭罪行"},{"pid":"9a51a3b346b771b30c0bb441a79aa365b1aeba48","tid":1447814,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:14:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣核彈 - 為恐怖主義正名</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEh1L51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEh1L51.jpg&h=6b5d83e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐怖主義標籤係諸國用嚟打壓異己嘅手法，「國家當局可用以將政敵或其他對手非法化，從而使國家武裝部隊可理直氣壯地打擊敵人」，包括支那對新疆嘅打壓，都係以打擊恐怖主義為名，效果顯著。若果我地為警隊嘅恐怖主義正名，絕對係致命打擊警隊嘅合法性同認受性嘅方法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別襲擊製造恐怖氣氛絕對已經係恐怖主義！我地係嘅係要為警隊嘅行為正名！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警隊失控無差別襲擊，係屬於國家恐怖主義嘅行為，已經超越「過度暴力」、「濫捕」同「濫用暴力」，依啲字眼淡化佢嘅「拐帶」、「恐怖襲擊」等非法行為，警隊嘅行為喺好多國家已經係可以定義為失去合法性啲武裝組織。<br />\n而且加上721恐襲同打後嘅黑警合作，有理由相信依個恐怖主義組織係跨越明同暗。現時警察喺民間嘅認受性極低，成為過街老鼠，執法行動已變質，失去合法地執行職務嘅能力，街坊見到警察嘅武裝會產生恐懼感。恐怖主義管治已引起社會及國際極度不安。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFFtbJu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFFtbJu.jpg&h=56511ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n-向民居、老人院、幼童出沒地點、葵芳地鐵站發射催淚神經毒劑，嚴重罔顧市民生命安全<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTDv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=b8e35ff2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">61,773</span>/100,000個簽名（12 Aug 2019 at 00:14）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作 恐怖治國<br />\n警察本色 恐怖組織</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">槍炮化武 無差別襲擊<br />\n警黑勾結 武裝巴結<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n821守衛香港 反警黑恐怖治國 反恐大遊行/集會（未定）<br />\n821 - 元朗恐襲紀念日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442294</a>"},{"pid":"25de7cdbc152fa46438f2dfc52155275f77cfd11","tid":1447814,"uid":269935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:14:31.000Z","msg":"佢地係野狗"},{"pid":"7e8b9fe541eda234e5d545d1f539ed91298e43b5","tid":1447814,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:15:35.000Z","msg":"要清除恐怖份子"},{"pid":"45b681fe9c3e8b0a20453a59f4473819d5e5e5e7","tid":1447814,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c977ec6b93cc83b3cdcf6dddd95e72de4fc5f75","tid":1447814,"uid":114798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:18:26.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n下次遊行試著叫恐怖分子<br />\n𣎴要叫黑社會"}]}